        {
            "title": "【一手速報】形瑨首批均呎17,177元貼市推！ 低同區新盤3.17%｜一房呎價高立坊6.25%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新地旗下荃灣形瑨今日（28日）公布首張價單，首推110伙。扣除最高15%折扣後，折實均呎約17,177元。由於荃灣區多年沒有新盤推出，是次首批單位定價稍為保守，具測試市場承接力之意。其折實均呎較同區上一個新盤低約3.17%；而一房入場單位的折實呎價，則較鄰近二手屋苑立坊近期的成交呎價高約6.25%。整體開價貼近區內一二手市場水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"形瑨價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:形瑨價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4w0ttx6\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">形瑨價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>首批110伙 折實約461萬起</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">項目首張價單推出110伙，涵蓋30伙一房及80伙兩房戶，實用面積介乎273至416平方呎。扣除最高15%折扣後，整批單位折實售價由461.46萬至736.44萬元，折實呎價介乎16,079至17,981元，折實均呎為17,177元。按定價計算，首批單位總值約8.15億元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4a018ed9-7290-318b-ad02-c8c997c16e11-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">入場單位方面，一房最低售價為5樓K室，實用面積273平方呎，折實約461.46萬元，折實呎價約16,903元。兩房最低售價為5樓N室，實用面積389平方呎，折實約628.15萬元，折實呎價約16,148元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按呎價計算，首批折實呎價最低為5樓M室兩房戶，實用面積393平方呎，折實呎價16,079元，折實售價約631.89萬元。折實呎價最高則為25樓J室一房戶，實用面積273平方呎，折實呎價17,981元，折實售價約490.87萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>形瑨首批開價 較同區映日灣稍低3.17%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荃灣區多年未有新盤推出，對上一個項目為2019年8月開售的映日灣。當年映日灣首推238伙，折實均呎為17,740元。相隔六年多，形瑨推出首批單位，折實均呎17,177元，開價較映日灣當年低約3.17%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交通方面，映日灣位置較為便利。項目步行約8分鐘可經有蓋天橋直達港鐵荃灣西站，沿途毋須日曬雨淋；附近亦設有荃灣西及如心廣場大型巴士總站，交通選擇較多，可往返港九新界多區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">形瑨距離港鐵荃灣西站、荃灣站或大窩口站步程約13至15分鐘，而且需途經露天街道。住戶日常出入較依賴區內巴士及小巴，交通便利程度與映日灣相比略有差距。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">生活配套方面，映日灣基座設有商場Plaza 88，並有行人天橋連接荃新天地及海之戀等商場，同時鄰近楊屋道街市，購物及飲食選擇較為集中。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">形瑨周邊以民生商舖為主，附近設有屋苑商場及悅來坊。如需前往大型商場或街市，步程約需10多分鐘，配套尚算齊備，但集中度不及映日灣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整體而言，形瑨首批單位開價與區內過往一手項目相比，屬貼市價，亦具相當吸引力。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2LFZoqiShN73LoomX.I5bQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/eafc715b54ddbe59b9033f278c15d3ca\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>形瑨與同區一手盤首推資料</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇映日灣最新放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇映日灣最新放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3P2avp7\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇映日灣最新放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房入場呎價較立坊近期成交高約6.25%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">形瑨與相距約7分鐘步程的立坊，同樣位處楊屋道及橫窩仔街一帶，鄰近工廠區，兩者的周邊環境及交通配套相若。參考<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse放盤紀錄\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse放盤紀錄;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4t5KhjB\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse放盤紀錄</a>，立坊現時約有30個放盤，實用面積介乎238至429平方呎，叫價由358萬至738萬元不等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參考近期成交，立坊一伙實用面積308平方呎的高層一房戶，以490萬元易手，實用呎價約15,909元。形瑨首批一房入場單位折實呎價為16,903元，較上述成交呎價高約6.25%，考慮到全新盤的優勢，定價屬貼近同區二手市場水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇立坊最新放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇立坊最新放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4t5KhjB\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇立坊最新放盤】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Agvbh6O9U2iQCK.2mU.IxA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/c6af4aab7daaf1d9b6dec12998d557ff\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>形瑨位於橫窩仔街，鄰近車房及工廠區，交通及民生配套不過不失。</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>銷售安排及項目背景</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新地代理特別發展部助理總經理（銷售及市務）譚錫湛表示，項目將於明日（29日）正式開放示範單位，周四（30日）起收票，有望最快於下月展開首輪銷售。他補充指，將視乎市場反應決定是否加推單位，並認為首張價單具競爭力，日後加推單位或會加價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由新鴻基地產發展的荃灣形瑨，位於橫窩仔街21號。項目建有1座住宅大樓，共提供462伙，實用面積介乎231至890平方呎。戶型涵蓋一至三房，另設特色單位；當中以兩房為主打，佔約70%，一房佔約20%，餘下為三房及特色戶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交通配套方面，由項目步行至港鐵荃灣站約需13至15分鐘。校網方面，小學屬於62校網，中學隸屬荃灣區。項目預計關鍵日期為2027年4月，樓花期約12個月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"形瑨\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:形瑨;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/形瑨\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">形瑨</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Plaza 88\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Plaza 88;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/Plaza-88-26160\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Plaza 88</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"如心廣場\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:如心廣場;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/office/detail/如心廣場-30423\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如心廣場</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"海之戀\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:海之戀;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/海之戀-27462\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">海之戀</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"立坊\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:立坊;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/立坊-4627\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">立坊</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"大窩口\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:大窩口;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/大窩口-27406\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">大窩口</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荃灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:荃灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/荃灣-27404\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">荃灣</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canv